## Early game

**Kadesh** on Mars (Dark Sector Defense) is an accessible early Fieldron
Sample spot. The wiki lists no mission or enemy drop table for this resource
at all — it's picked up as an environmental resource item scattered through
the Dark Sector tileset, so simply exploring the level between Defense waves
matters more than kill count.

## Mid & late game

**Kelashin** on Neptune (Dark Sector Survival) is the wiki's recommended
endgame spot. Running it in Steel Path mainly buys a squad more time to sweep
the Infested Ship tileset for pickups on a longer Survival timer — since
Fieldron Sample is neither an enemy drop nor a resource cache, Resource Drop
Boosters and the Steel Path passive don't change how often it turns up.
Thorough exploration, not drop-chance buffs, is what raises the count here.

